title: Germany: Pep Guardiola defends Catalonian independence in "Guanyarem" campaign
description:
In footage released on Tuesday, Bayern Munich's manager and former FC Barcelona's manager and player Pep Guardiola spoke about Catalonian independence as part of the "Guanyarem" campaign supporting Catalan sports in Munich.
